ntroduced on pull request #2916 for example could be a scene plugin.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>On Gazebo rendering, there's already a <code>VisualPlugin</code>, but it would be also nice to have a plugin type in rendering which is tied to the <code>rendering::Scene</code> itself and not a single visual. It would be analogous to how we have <code>ModelPlugin</code>s and <code>WorldPlugin</code>s in physics.</p>\n<p>The plugin introduced on <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2916/add-screen-space-ambient-occlusion-visual\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">pull request #2916</a> for example could be a scene plugin.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "new", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2018-05-02T23:26:38.266256+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2018-05-02T23:26:38.266256+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 2468}